summary.para: The CRYPT_CONTENT_INFO_SEQUENCE_OF_ANY structure contains information representing the Netscape certificate sequence of certificates.
A Netscape certificate sequence of certificates can be created by setting the pszObjId member to szOID_NETSCAPE_CERT_SEQUENCE and supplying DER-encoded certificates in rgValue.

member.name: CRYPT_CONTENT_INFO_SEQUENCE_OF_ANY.pszObjId
member.summary: Object identifier (OID) specifying the type of data contained in the rgValue array.

member.name: CRYPT_CONTENT_INFO_SEQUENCE_OF_ANY.cValue
member.summary: Number of elements in the rgValue array.

member.name: CRYPT_CONTENT_INFO_SEQUENCE_OF_ANY.rgValue
member.summary: Array of pointers to CRYPT_DER_BLOB structures. For more information, seeCRYPT_INTEGER_BLOB.
